text: Jörg Schramme is a sailor from Germany. Schramme competed at the 1976 Summer Olympics and the 1980 Summer Olympics. He was born on 25 December 1951.Jörg Schramme == References == Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Sailors Category:Olympians for East Germany Category:Sportspeople from Leipzig
